c: 9
v: 5
t: "Ngakho-ke uma sekudlule izinyanga ezingcwele seningababulala abakhonzi bezithixo noma ngabe yikuphi lapho nibathola khona futhi nibathumbe futhi nibavimbele nihlale nibalindele kuzona zonke izindawo zokucasha kepha uma bezisola futhi benza imithandazo futhi bekhokha izakaah (ingxenye yengcebo ekhokhelwa abampofu) iyekeni indlela yabo ikhululekile, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyathethelela unesihawu"